ing: 1 (16 ounce) package frozen mixed vegetables, thawed
2 (16 ounce) cans Italian-style diced tomatoes, drained
des: "Sauteed chicken breasts braised in tomatoes and veggies, all in one skillet, all in one step. Serve over white or brown rice."
ins: Melt butter or margarine in a large skillet over medium high heat. Add chicken and saute for about 4 to 5 minutes, until lightly browned. Add mixed vegetables and tomatoes, reduce heat to low and simmer for 30 to 40 minutes, or until chicken is cooked through and no longer pink inside.
